Subject: grr: ASE Linux Server

Based on core-image-full-cmdline.

Runs within the simulation environment (ASE) to provide dhcp,
tftp, and the simicsfs client.

Simics archive should be copied to the poky directory and
the version should be set in local.conf via SIMICS_VERSION
variable.

If simics isn't available, comment out the IMAGE_INSTALL:append
line in local.conf that adds simicsfs-client etc.

